Application
	Update queue (merge regions)
	
Layouts
	HBox, VBox and Grid optimisations.
	Handle min/max in Grid.

Image and Video
	Animated icons
	GStreamer/FFMpeg controller

Widgets
	ToolBar
	List
	Table
	
Maestro
	Fullscreen application mode
	Single instance of Designer.

Command line options
